<div id="infobox" class="infobox"> 
 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Black Flame Blade</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="black_flame_blade_incantation_spell_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/black_flame_blade_incantation_spell_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="black flame blade incantation spell elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godskin Apostle Incantations" href="/Godskin+Apostle+Incantations" target="">Godskin Apostle Incantations</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost 15</td> 
     <td>Slots Used 1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Enchants right-hand armament with black flame 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a> 0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a> 17 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Black Flame Blade</strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Black Flame Blade </strong>temporarily envelops your right-hand weapon in a black flame, increasing damage.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>A black flame incantation of the Godskin Apostles.<br></em></p> 
 <p><em>Engulfs armament held in the right hand with black flame. This incantation can be cast without delay after performing another action.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Black flame is weighty. After dealing damage it continues to sap foes' HP for a very short time.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Black Flame Blade</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Black Flame Blade</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>This incantation is&nbsp;unlocked for purchase after&nbsp;giving a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godskin Prayerbook" href="/Godskin+Prayerbook" target="">Godskin Prayerbook</a> to <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Brother Corhyn" href="/Brother+Corhyn" target="">Brother Corhyn</a>&nbsp;or <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Miriel Pastor of Vows" href="/Miriel+Pastor+of+Vows"> Miriel, Pastor of Vows </a>.</li> 
</ul> 
<p><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godskin Prayerbook" href="/Godskin+Prayerbook" target="">Godskin Prayerbook</a>&nbsp;Location:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Location:&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stormveil Castle" href="/Stormveil+Castle" target="">Stormveil Castle</a></li> 
 <li>Nearest Site of Grace:&nbsp;Liftside Chamber</li> 
 <li>From the arch doorway exiting to the courtyard, head straight into the area with all the enemies and hug the right side and you'll see a set of stairs that goes underground.<br><img title="thisway_godskin_prayerbook" src="/file/Elden-Ring/thisway_godskin_prayerbook.png" alt="thisway godskin prayerbook" width="378" height="269"></li> 
 <li>You'll find a room that is guarded by four <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Giant Rat" href="/Giant+Rat">Giant Rats</a>, and ahead, is a doorway that is blocked by a white fog. To dispel this, you will need to use a&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stonesword Key" href="/Stonesword+Key" target="">Stonesword Key</a>&nbsp;on the Imp Statue.&nbsp;You'll find&nbsp;a stock room upon unlocking the doorway,&nbsp;which has a treasure chest holding the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godskin Prayerbook" href="/Godskin+Prayerbook">Godskin Prayerbook</a>, and another chest holding the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godslayer's Seal" href="/Godslayer's+Seal">Godslayer's Seal</a>.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Black Flame Blade Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godskin Apostle Incantations" href="/Godskin+Apostle+Incantations" target="">Godskin Apostle Incantation</a> 
  <ul> 
   <li>Howver, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">neither</span> its fire damage nor its DoT effect are boosted by the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godslayer's Seal" href="/Godslayer's+Seal" target="">Godslayer's Seal</a>.</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
 <li>Buffs weapon with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Fire Damage" href="/Fire+Damage">Fire attack power</a></li> 
 <li>Fire: 0.65 * Incant Scaling (Faith portion)</li> 
 <li>Duration: 7 seconds</li> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 10</li> 
 <li>Black Flame Blade has a very short duration but fairly quick cast time (especially between actions) similar to Drawstring Grease, and should be used immediately before&nbsp;attacking, or between attacks for a continued combo.</li> 
 <li>Puts a 2 second damage over time effect on enemies struck while the buff is active. Dealing 20 damage plus 20 more for every 1000 HP the enemy has. This results in at least 2% of Max HP or more damage over time.</li> 
 <li>This burning effect does not scale or stack, but is refreshed with each hit.</li> 
 <li>The burning effect can be applied using weapon skills.</li> 
</ul> 
<div style="max-width: 560px; max-height: 316px;"> 
